    "name": "DEEPEST FEAR™ - 最深的恐惧",
    "steam_appid": 2334930,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334930/extras/3f74eae3343c14fdc2ff211395b52f6f.poster.avif?t=1763125751\" width=628 height=182 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334930/extras/3f74eae3343c14fdc2ff211395b52f6f.webm?t=1763125751\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334930/extras/3f74eae3343c14fdc2ff211395b52f6f.mp4?t=1763125751\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>DEEPEST FEAR™</strong> 是一款具有复古未来美学的科幻恐怖第一人称射击游戏。深海之下，一项长眠已久的秘密被发现，将人类的未来置于危险之中。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >深入深渊</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334930/extras/5ae8d1b974e9616f633eee0f7a2bbf82.poster.avif?t=1763125751\" width=628 height=182 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334930/extras/5ae8d1b974e9616f633eee0f7a2bbf82.webm?t=1763125751\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334930/extras/5ae8d1b974e9616f633eee0f7a2bbf82.mp4?t=1763125751\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >扮演丹尼·卡罗尔博士，冲破障碍，深入一个由你疏远的父亲策划的秘密项目的核心，揭开既深刻又令人恐惧的谜团。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >恐惧之水</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334930/extras/da73ac25275edb12739ac8db96bbc019.poster.avif?t=1763125751\" width=628 height=182 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334930/extras/da73ac25275edb12739ac8db96bbc019.webm?t=1763125751\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334930/extras/da73ac25275edb12739ac8db96bbc019.mp4?t=1763125751\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用实时流体模拟技术，与那些从任何水源中自发显现的异界生物战斗。与此同时，你周围的环境可能随时被洪水淹没，将你卷入不可预测的水流中，拖入令人窒息的深渊。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >沉浸式模拟 + 类银河恶魔城</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334930/extras/5dabd72da636ca210eb9203669233cc8.poster.avif?t=1763125751\" width=628 height=182 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334930/extras/5dabd72da636ca210eb9203669233cc8.webm?t=1763125751\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334930/extras/5dabd72da636ca210eb9203669233cc8.mp4?t=1763125751\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Deepest Fear 将类银河恶魔城的关卡设计与经典 FPS 沉浸式模拟结合起来，使游戏场景成为一个需要解开的谜题，而你的创造力和即兴能力是最重要的武器。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >复古未来主义的恐怖</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334930/extras/5d2cebe28836bc131e17f18c7b4ab7c7.poster.avif?t=1763125751\" width=628 height=182 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334930/extras/5d2cebe28836bc131e17f18c7b4ab7c7.webm?t=1763125751\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334930/extras/5d2cebe28836bc131e17f18c7b4ab7c7.mp4?t=1763125751\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >致敬如《深渊》、《怪形》、《苍蝇》、《全面回忆》等标志性、颠覆性的1980年代恐怖动作电影，以及詹姆斯·卡梅隆、约翰·卡朋特、大卫·柯南伯格、保罗·范霍文等导演的作品，Deepest Fear 力求忠实于其灵感来源，将感官恐惧、生动的角色塑造与大胆的叙事结合。同时，在互动方面，我们从《银河战士Prime》、《半条命2》、《网络奇兵2》和《死亡空间》等游戏中汲取灵感。</p>",
